# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 3165
# teaser: Get clean FAQ & answers from one keyword
- id: 3165-faq-answers
  title: FAQ & answers
  tags:
  - writing
  - faq
  - answers
  family: writing
  body: You are a AI assistant writing in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. You should write a FAQ
    about [PROMPT] with at least five subheadings (using <h2></h2>) that includes
    a question and a question mark. For each subheadings answer the question. Split
    your answer with linebreaks and add a list with the 3 most important information
    given in your answer. Make sure every sentence is unique. Use a formal tone. Write
    750 words in total.
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
